From what you have there I think you can get this done quickly by using a foreach enumerator with a data flow task inside it.  Each iteration of the foreach on an mdb file would set a variable as the source of the data flow task.  if the mappings are completely different on the mdb&#039;s you may be better off getting the mdbs into a directory in which the mappings all match or create a script task to set the mappings in the foreach.&lt;br /&gt;
